{"tid":2372120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗4歲男童今日生日 嘔吐昏迷搶救不治","createTime":"2021-01-19T11:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T12:57:36.000Z","uid":10540,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6a81a1424f0f53789d70c1fa78706a12f7de51","tid":2372120,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"下午4時許。深水埗南昌街105號唐樓4樓一單位，一名4歲男童被發現昏迷在屋內，救護員到場後，隨即將他送往明愛醫院搶救，惜回天乏術，警方在現場調查事件，事後帶走一名女子及一名8歲男童返警署協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n4歲男童曾在上周三（13日）及上周六（16日），在父母陪同下，分別到私家醫生及明愛醫院，就腸胃炎求診，當時檢測對武肺病毒呈陰性。至今日下午兩時許開始，男童開始乏力，但仍有知覺，至下午3時許起身食粥食藥，豈料嘔吐大作，其後昏迷，送院搶救惜告不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210119/MJ374HWSMFB6ZE42FK3HP5AMZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210119%2FMJ374HWSMFB6ZE42FK3HP5AMZA%2F&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=de0c9d72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210119%2FMJ374HWSMFB6ZE42FK3HP5AMZA%2F&h=3605eec7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210119/MJ374HWSMFB6ZE42FK3HP5AMZA/</a>"},{"pid":"78d16831ea01505f9ae9f6dfec88cca7c1a4522c","tid":2372120,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"落毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d8504899c33d749472e59e694506af978577d8","tid":2372120,"uid":167931,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a637019ddc5b8dec6aa92e4bdedd5375ee18eb5","tid":2372120,"uid":13149,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"好事黎 快D投胎"},{"pid":"ca369e4a09